text: Angelina Pivarnick (born June 26, 1986) is an American television personality. She is best known for starring in the first two seasons of the MTV's reality show Jersey Shore and the VH1 show Couples Therapy. Pivarnick made her return to television in Jersey Shore: Family Vacation. She was born in Staten Island, New York. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Television personalities from New York City
